vernment employees think they are U.S. spies, only to discover that they are actually decoys for nuclear war.","genre_ids":[35,12],"popularity":2.4943,"vote_count":686,"poster_path":"/s0Sx8nd9Irq0aCPbsN78s0DYVlG.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-06","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/9RJGN6CaCFOzs9H1yie2aPxLUoX.jpg","original_title":"Spies Like Us","original_language":"en"},{"id":9104,"adult":false,"title":"Buffalo Soldiers","video":false,"overview":"A criminal subculture operates among U.S. soldiers stationed in West Germany just before the fall of the Berlin wall.","genre_ids":[18,35,10752,80,53],"popularity":4.5892,"vote_count":345,"poster_path":"/qNl4T8xxC0xDeX8JFJVCBzH4Kg8.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":6.286,"backdrop_path":"/7Pw5NOv7aUtmHyh1yASEldOlAz0.jpg","original_title":"Buffalo Soldiers","original_language":"en"},{"id":9259,"adult":false,"title":"Bibi Blocksberg","video":false,"overview":"Elation in Neustadt: by the means of a little witching, Bibi Blocksberg saved two kids from burning to death. While her mother Barbara, a witch of flesh and blood herself, is very proud of her daughter, father Bernhard, overworked and stressed, disapproves greatly of her supernatural antics. Then Bibi gets a message from Walpurgia, the senior witch: she is going to receive her crystel ball, that will make a \"real\" witch of her, early. Proudly, Bibi jumps up her broom to fly to the Blocksberg, the witches' headquarters. But Rabia, one of the few evil witches, aging in misery and with a secret, begrudges her all the glory...and her youth. And so Rabia sets off events that will soon make Bibi's life fall into pieces.","genre_ids":[12,35,10751,14],"popularity":4.936,"vote_count":86,"poster_path":"/9r7epbLqqtjtlkvRpCwVHIiGkB.jpg","release_date":"2002-09-25","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/oApE6TUeteedCL3CP1d8pCVfq0X.jpg","original_title":"Bibi Blocksberg","original_language":"de"},{"id":9278,"adult":false,"title":"Freejack","video":false,"overview":"Time